      "rationale": "The observational flow-loop study covered all five target operating points and maintained nominally constant conditions within each facility. However, conditions were not prospectively randomised, confounding variables across facilities were not formally controlled, and sample analysis was not blinded. The study satisfies an observational-study standard but falls short of the controlled-experiment protocol required at MRL-5. Achieved level 3; required level 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
